<h3 id="generate-a-landscape">Generate a Landscape</h3>

<p>Int íƒ€ì…ì˜ ë°°ì—´ì„ ì´ìš©í•˜ì—¬ landscapeì„ ìƒì„±í•´ ë´…ë‹ˆë‹¤.</p>

<div class="language-swift highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  <span class="c1">// ê° ì¸ë±ìŠ¤ì— í• ë‹¹ë˜ì–´ ìˆëŠ” ê°’ì— ì ‘ê·¼í•˜ê¸°</span>
  <span class="k">var</span> <span class="nv">heights</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">]</span>
